The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Sports | KP PRAISE FOR GOSWAMI
                                                     KP PRAISE FOR GOSWAMI
                              
	Kevin Pietersen, who captained the Royal Challengers Bangalore till Wednesdays match against the Kolkata Knight Riders, showered much praise on young Sreevats Goswami, the Bengal player who was one of the heroes of Indias U-19 World Cup win early last year.         
	The following are excerpts from what he said at the media conference:         
	Sreevats is a fantastic little character... Hes such a good cricketer... Id say hes a little gem... He gave me the most advice on the field and what a great catch he took of (Chris) Gayle...           OUR SPECIAL CORRESPONDENT IN DURBAN                                                                                                                   
